{"tid":1862541,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解！燕京書院？曾經我以為做得校長 有學歷都會有反個腦 點知⋯⋯","createTime":"2020-02-04T16:16:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T18:42:10.000Z","uid":311942,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f13e7a93aa9a15d4d6b91a19ebab40ba12ebaa74","tid":1862541,"uid":311942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T16:16:23.000Z","msg":"中華基督教會燕京書院 校長原來無腦加廢柴<br />\n原來梁振狗嘅奶鞋撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n夏麗珠垃圾校長，我都知你想出下名，刷下存在感ok無問題！就比你出下名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拿！人做校長佢做校長，有d就真係帶住個腦愛學生嘅<br />\n<br />\n假假地一個校長都有反博士級水平嘅學歷<br />\n<br />\n點知我個世界觀係而一年內 反轉左幾次⋯⋯好亂丫！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拿！今日同大家介紹一個博士級校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢真係有博士學歷架，但我就估係買 一係假 一係吹反黎<br />\n⋯不過而個世界咩博士都有，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有真博士同假卜士<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n葛X帆已完，就真係假卜士啦，大家一樣無腦同冷血<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邊d巴打同C打，而間讀過書嘅，幫幫手郵寄送反佢去武漢。感受下病毒嘅殺傷力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中華基督教會燕京書院藍絲校長夏麗珠冷血言論<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ejdPAcx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FejdPAcx.jpg&h=51a5386d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kLOgfcx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkLOgfcx.jpg&h=4cd6c005&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9pghJ5T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9pghJ5T.jpg&h=60456e9a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dkAitxy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdkAitxy.jpg&h=ae6c4ca1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f5500b868b1fcf352195281a8bfcf879fdbc634","tid":1862541,"uid":311942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T00:51:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3b32874d244725743d2e39ecdf5defb1dcec42f","tid":1862541,"uid":314767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T18:16:07.000Z","msg":"由佢話要整白鴿嗰陣開始 我已經知佢係冇腦啦<br />\n辛苦你地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88450e36a5a0fd0838aaf60e12eab35d469a123f","tid":1862541,"uid":311942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3b32874d244725743d2e39ecdf5defb1dcec42f","tid":1862541,"uid":314767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T18:16:07.000Z","msg":"由佢話要整白鴿嗰陣開始 我已經知佢係冇腦啦<br />\n辛苦你地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T18:42:10.000Z","msg":"咁都做到校長⋯⋯"}]}